Please read the README and INSTALL files first.

You only need the information in this file when working on non-released
versions of DynamiTE. Installation information for released versions
of DynamiTE can be found in the INSTALL file.

To build:
	1) Run ./autogen.sh
	2) Run ./configure with appropriate options
	3) make
	4) make install

